<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The code calls mhd_assert(0) after the switch. The macro will expand to a conditional/controlling construct that tests the constant expression 0 (invariant). This uses an invariant controlling expression (a constant false) for error handling/reachability checking rather than for an allowed infinite loop/do-while constant-false exception, so it violates MISRA C 2023 Rule 14.3.
</scenario>

